wiki.content:
Out of Control was the first single released by the American alternative rock band Hoobastank from their highly successful album The Reason. It charted at #16 on the US Mainstream Rock charts and at #9 on the US Modern Rock charts.
 
 The song also features backing vocals by Ian Watkins and Jamie Oliver of the Welsh alternative metal band Lostprophets.
